ZH: 我家屋顶上长满了青苔。
EN: The roof of my house is covered with moss.

ZH: 森林里到处都是青苔。
EN: There is moss everywhere in the forest.

ZH: 雨后，公园的石头上长满了青苔。
EN: After the rain, the stones in the park are covered in moss.

ZH: 这块墙上的青苔很养眼。
EN: The moss on this wall is very pleasing to the eye.

ZH: 青苔给这个古墓带来了一种神秘感。
EN: The moss gives this ancient tomb a sense of mystery.

ZH: 在农田里，青苔可以保持土壤湿润。
EN: In farmlands, moss can help to retain soil moisture.

ZH: 这片青苔覆盖的地面看起来很柔软。
EN: The ground covered in moss looks very soft.

ZH: 青苔可以吸收大气中的水分和养分。
EN: Moss can absorb water and nutrients from the air.

ZH: 青苔可以生长在石头、树木和土壤上。
EN: Moss can grow on rocks, trees, and soil.

ZH: 野外的石头上经常可以看到青苔。
EN: Moss is often seen on rocks in the wild.

ZH: 这个花盆里生出了一些小小的青苔。
EN: Some tiny mosses have grown in this flowerpot.

ZH: 青苔在潮湿的环境中生长得更好。
EN: Moss grows better in moist environments.

ZH: 青苔可以防止水土流失。
EN: Moss can prevent soil erosion.

ZH: 青苔在生态系统中扮演着重要的角色。
EN: Moss plays an important role in ecosystems.

ZH: 这个古老的城堡墙上覆盖着厚厚的青苔。
EN: The walls of this ancient castle are covered with thick moss.

ZH: 青苔给庭院增添了一份自然的美丽。
EN: The moss adds a natural beauty to the courtyard.

ZH: 青苔的触感很柔软，有些人喜欢赤足在上面走。
EN: Moss feels soft to touch, and some people enjoy walking barefoot on it.

ZH: 这片森林地面上到处都是湿滑的青苔。
EN: The forest floor is slippery with moss everywhere.

ZH: 一阵清风吹过，将树林里的青苔吹得飘起来。
EN: A gust of wind blows and lifts the moss off the trees in the forest.

ZH: 这块老房子的屋顶上已长满了青苔，需要清理了。
EN: The roof of this old house is covered with moss and needs cleaning.
